	"summary": "Moderate: gdk-pixbuf2 security update",
	"details": "The gdk-pixbuf2 packages provide an image loading library that can be extended\nby loadable modules for new image formats. It is used by toolkits such as GTK+\nor clutter.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\n* gdk-pixbuf2: heap memory corruption on gdk-pixbuf (CVE-2022-48622)\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS\nscore, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.",
